        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The thing to note isn't how disciplined I am for having written so consistently for all this time, or even how difficult doing something like this",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "must",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "have been.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The thing worth exploring, the thing worth pondering, is how",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "easy",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "it's been. Far easier than I ever would have thought, starting out.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I don't ask myself",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\"should I write something today?”",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ", as I go about my day. In fact, I don't even ask",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "“what should I write about?”",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I just",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "do",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It's literally",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "out of the question",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ". I'm going to write something and the only thing worth thinking about is",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "what",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
